Create an expense sharing application.

An expense sharing application is where you can add your expenses and split it among different people.
The app keeps balances between people as in who owes how much to whom.

Api
/register -> (User);
/addFriends -> (List<userId>);
/split -> equal, percent, ratio, manual. option to add friends to split with, add notes
/showExpense /{userId}->
/history/{userId}


User{
    userId
    name
    phone
    email
    balance
    List<User> friends
}

enum SplitType {
    EQUAL,
    PERCENT,
    RATIO,
    MANUAL
}

Expense{
    expenseId
    User paidBy
    int amount
    HashMap<User, int> cashSpent
}

History{
    historyId
    List<Expense> expenses
}